title: Essinth Furryart October 2007
description:
Essinth&#039;s Furry Art Collection. October 2007.

The best of the best, from Essinth&#039;s point of view. If the picture&#039;s content is good, but drawn badly, it gets trashed. If the picture is drawn well but that&#039;s just it - only drawn well, it gets trashed, too. So, over time, the collection just gets better.

The collection is categorised, 0 means non-adult and mostly safe for work, everything above - adult. Which category picture belongs to was intuitively chosen, no strict rules.

Now this collection has an extra category set -- which starts with "a". That used to be for anime-related art, but now it&#039;s for anything that&#039;s not furry.
